1
00:00:01,042 --> 00:00:02,127
TAKESHI OHYAMA

2
00:00:02,210 --> 00:00:05,547
Semuanya bermula dengan kasus
pekosaan geng Musashino.

3
00:00:05,630 --> 00:00:07,006
Ada sesuatu yang ingin kuberikan.

4
00:00:07,090 --> 00:00:08,216
Ini bukti.

5
00:00:08,299 --> 00:00:09,718
Kakakku hendak dibunuh!

6
00:00:09,801 --> 00:00:10,760
Sersan Ohyama?

7
00:00:11,553 --> 00:00:13,179
Sersan Ohyama!

8
00:00:41,249 --> 00:00:42,542
Ohyama

9
00:00:43,376 --> 00:00:44,586
seharusnya sudah mati.

10
00:00:48,798 --> 00:00:50,133
Dia masih hidup

11
00:00:53,928 --> 00:00:55,221
di radio ini.

12
00:00:56,431 --> 00:00:57,474
Itu dia!

13
00:01:01,561 --> 00:01:02,854
Kento Saegusa,

14
00:01:02,937 --> 00:01:05,398
kau ditangkap
atas pembunuhan Kepala Iwata.

15
00:01:05,482 --> 00:01:06,357
Apa yang terjadi?

16
00:01:06,775 --> 00:01:08,526
Kami punya bukti dan saksi mata.

17
00:01:08,610 --> 00:01:09,527
Bukti?

18
00:01:09,652 --> 00:01:12,030
Sidik jarimu ditemukan
di senjata pembunuhan,

19
00:01:12,697 --> 00:01:14,157
yang ada di kamar mandi rumah sakit.

20
00:01:15,200 --> 00:01:16,242
Mustahil.

21
00:01:16,326 --> 00:01:17,911
Kami akan cari tahu

22
00:01:17,994 --> 00:01:19,454
yang kalian lakukan di sini.

23
00:01:21,539 --> 00:01:22,373
Hei!

24
00:01:22,791 --> 00:01:23,750
Berhenti!

25
00:01:23,833 --> 00:01:25,293
Berhenti!

26
00:01:26,586 --> 00:01:28,129
Target melarikan diri lewat gedung!

27
00:01:28,213 --> 00:01:29,714
Aku butuh bantuan!

28
